item.title: Project Dossier
item.description: Dossier A reporting and analytics platform Scope of work: It is a service or web application which is responsible for providing data to concerned party.The concerned parties beside sales and management also include HR, OPS, General Sales Manager(GSM), other services like SPEAR. It is helpful to people in following ways- It shall allow partners to see their business and be motivated. It shall allow management to see business stats and analyse and make decisions.
